summary:
I am an ambitious, results-oriented, dedicated professional with excellent communication skills, sharp networking abilities, and an innate desire to consistently seek out the next challenge.  

Passionate about procurement, sales, recruitment, and customer-facing roles, I am dedicated to utilizing my assets to help contribute to the growth and success of your company.

With almost 2 years of experience working in Procurement as a Supplier Manager, I have been faced with a plethora of opportunities to:
- Sharpen my communication skills
- Explore the most effective practices for optimizing supplier relationships
- Utilize my negotiation capabilities to ensure the most cost-effective solutions are realized

I excel in building, and maintaining, fruitful relationships both internally, and externally. 
I thrive in a fast-paced, target-driven environment, and remain focused on delivering exceptional results consistently. 
I am not only focused on building strong external relationships, but also establishing collaborative relationships internally with colleagues. 
I believe these skills will be advantageous not only in the field of Procurement, but also Sales, Recruitment and customer-facing roles. 

If you are seeking a dedicated professional who thrives on a challenge, and who has a passion for growth in the fields of procurement, sales & recruitment, then I invite you to connect. I look forward to exploring how my skillset and experience can contribute to your organization's continued growth and success, together. 

E-mail: auxanaisakendall@gmail.com
Mobile: +31 6 420 933 68
